;Geolocation in Firefox
Geò-lorgadh ann am Firefox


;Location-Aware Browsing
Brabhsadh a mhothaicheas dha d' àite


;Firefox can tell websites where you’re located so you can find info that’s more relevant and more useful. It’s about making the Web smarter &ndash; and is done in a way that totally respects your privacy. <a href="%(url)s" id="%(id)s">Give it a try!</a>
'S urrainn dha Firefox innse do làraichean-lìn càit a bheil thu airson 's gum faigh thu fiosrachadh a tha iomchaidh dhan àite far a bheil thu. Eadar-lìon nas glice, mar gum biodh &ndash; agus air dòigh a dhìonas do phrìobhaideachd fhathast. <a href="%(url)s" id="%(id)s">Siuthad, feuch e!</a>


;Frequently asked Questions
CÀBHA - Na Ceistean Àbhaisteach


;What is Location-Aware Browsing?
Dè th' ann am brabhsadh a mhothaicheas dha m' àite?


;Websites that use location-aware browsing will ask where you are in order to bring you more relevant information, or to save you time while searching. Let’s say you’re looking for a pizza restaurant in your area. A website will be able to ask you to share your location so that simply searching for “pizza” will bring you the answers you need... no further information or extra typing required.
Mas urrainn dha làrach-lìn mothachadh dhan àite far a bheil thu, faighnichidh i dhen bhrabhsair càit a bheil thu airson ùine a shàbhaladh dhut. Can gu bheil thu a' lorg taigh pizza 'nad sgìre. Ma tha fios aig làrach-lìn càit a bheil thu, cha leig thu leas ach am facal "pizza" a chur a-steach agus gheibh thu taighean pizza 'nad sgìre-sa... gun fheum air barrachd fiosrachaidh no taidhpidh.


;Or, if you’re mapping out directions to get somewhere, the website will know where you’re starting from so all you have to do is tell it where you want to go.
No ma tha thu a' sireadh stiùireadh a dh'àite air choireigin, bidh fios aig an làrach-lìn càit a bheil thu a' tòiseachadh air do thuras agus cha leig thu leas ach innse dha càit a bheil thu a' dol.


;This service is totally optional &ndash; Firefox doesn’t share your location without your permission &ndash; and is done with the utmost respect for your privacy. And, like all elements of Firefox, it’s being created using open standards to ease adoption by Web developers.
'S e seirbheis gu tur roghainneil a tha seo &ndash; cha nochd Firefox d' ionad gun chead uat &ndash; agus bidh sinn fhathast a' làn-dìon do phrìobhaideachd. Agus, mar a tha e le co-phàirt sam bith de Firefox, tha sinn 'ga chruthachadh stèidhichte air stannardan fosgailte airson 's gum bi e furasta do luchd-leasachaidh an eadar-lìn a chur gu feum.


;How does it work?
Ciamar a dh'obraicheas e?


;When you visit a location-aware website, Firefox will ask you if you want to share your location.
Ma thadhlas tu air làrach-lìn as urrainn dha mothachadh dha d' ionad, faighnichidh Firefox a bheil thu airson d' ionad a nochdadh ris.


;If you consent, Firefox gathers information about nearby wireless access points and your computer’s IP address. Then Firefox sends this information to the default geolocation service provider, Google Location Services, to get an estimate of your location. That location estimate is then shared with the requesting website.
Ma dh'aontaicheas tu ris, cruinnichidh Firefox fiosrachadh a thaobh nam puingean inntrigidh uèirleas a tha faisg ort agus seòladh IP a' choimpiutair agad. Cuiridh Firefox am fiosrachadh seo do sholaraiche bunaiteach na seirbheise geò-lorgaidh, Google Location Services, airson tuairmeas fhaighinn air d' ionad. Agus thèid an tuairmeas seo a nochdadh ris an làrach-lìn a dh'iarr d' ionad an uairsin.


;If you say that you do not consent, Firefox will not do anything.
Ma dhiùltas tu seo, cha dèan Firefox dad.


;How accurate are the locations?
Dè cho pongail 's a tha na h-ionadan seo?


;Accuracy varies greatly from location to location. In some places, our service providers may be able to provide a location to within a few meters. However, in other areas it might be much more than that. All locations returned by our service providers are estimates only and we do not guarantee the accuracy of the locations provided. Please do not use this information for emergencies. Always use common sense.
Tha a' phongalachd a' crochadh air an àite far a bheil thu. Ann an cuid a dh'àitichean bidh seo gu math pongail, beagan mheatairean air falbh uat. Ach cha bhi e cho pongail ann an àitichean eile. Chan eil sna h-ionadan uile ach tuairmeasan a thug solaraiche na seirbheise dhuinn agus chan urrainn dhuinn barantas a thoirt gum bi iad seo buileach ceart. Cha bu chòir dhut am fiosrachadh seo a chleachdadh ann an èiginn - bidh toinisgeil d' a thaobh an-còmhnaidh.


;What information is being sent, and to whom? How is my privacy protected?
Dè am fiosrachadh a tha 'ga chur 's cò thuige? Ciamar a tha sibh a' dìon mo phrìobhaideachd?


;Your privacy is extremely important to us, and Firefox never shares your location without your permission. When you visit a page that requests your information, you’ll be asked before any information is shared with the requesting website and our third-party service provider.
Tha do phrìobhaideachd air leth cudromach dhuinn agus cha nochd Firefox d' ionad idir gun aonta uat. Ma thadhlas tu air duilleag a tha ag iarraidh fiosrachadh uat, faighnichidh sinn dhìot mus dèid dad a nochdadh ris an làrach-lìn a dh'iarr e agus ris an t-solaraiche treas-phàrtaidh againn.


;By default, Firefox uses Google Location Services to determine your location by sending:
Cleachdaidh Firefox Google Location Services a ghnàth airson tuairmeas a dhèanamh air d' ionad is e a' cur:


;your computer’s IP address,
seòladh IP a' choimpiutair agad,


;information about the nearby wireless access points, and
fiosrachadh mu na puingean inntrigidh uèirleas faisg ort agus


;a random client identifier, which is assigned by Google, that expires every 2 weeks.
aithnichear cliaint air thuaiream a thèid iomruineadh le Google agus a dh'fhalbhas an ùine air gach cola-deug.


;For a complete description of information collected and used by Firefox, please see the <a href="%(url)s">Firefox Privacy Notice</a>.
Airson tuairisgeul mionaideach air an fhiosrachadh a chruinnicheas is a chleachdas Firefox, thoir sùil air <a href="%(url)s">sanas prìobhaideachd Firefox</a>.


;Google Location Services then returns your estimated geolocation (e.g., latitude and longitude). For a complete description of information collected and used by Google, please see the <a href="%(url)s" class="%(class)s">Google Geolocation Privacy Policy</a>.
Bheir Google Location Services dhuinn tuairmeas air an àite far a bheil thu ('s e sin an domhan-leud agus an domhan-fhad). Airson tuairisgeul mionaideach air an fhiosrachadh a chruinnicheas is a chleachdas Google, thoir sùil air <a href="%(url)s" class="%(class)s">poileasaidh prìobhaideachd Google a thaobh geò-lorgaidh</a>.


;The information is exchanged over an encrypted connection to protect your privacy. Once Firefox has your location information, it passes it to the website that requested it. At no time is the name or location of the website you are visiting, or are any cookies, ever shared with Google Location Services.
Thèid am fiosrachadh seo a chur air ceangal crioptaichte gus do phrìobhaideachd a dhìon. Turas a gheibh Firefox am fiosrachadh mu d' ionad, sìnidh e seo air adhart dhan làrach-lìn a dh'iarr e. Cha dèid ainm no ionad na làraich-lìn air a bheil thu a' tadhal no briosgaid sam bith a' nochdadh dha Google Location Services idir aig àm sam bith.


;Neither Mozilla or Google will ever use the information collected by Google Location Services to identify or spy on you.
Cha chleachd Mozilla no Google am fiosrachadh a chruinnicheas Google Location Services gu sìorraidh bràth gus d' aithneachadh gu pearsanta no airson brathadh ort.


;For information about what the requesting website does with your location information, please refer to that website’s privacy policy.
A thaobh na nì an làrach-lìn fhèin leis an fhiosrachadh mu d' ionad, bu chòir dhut sùil a thoirt air poileasaidh prìobhaideachd na làraich fhèin.


;For more information about your privacy, you should also read:
Airson barrachd fiosrachaidh mu do phrìobhaideachd, bu chòir dhut sùil a thoirt air na leanas cuideachd:


;Mozilla Firefox Privacy Notice
Aithris prìobhaideachd Mozilla Firefox


;Google privacy policy
Poileasaidh prìobhaideachd Google


;Am I being tracked as I browse the web?
A bheilear 'gam thracadh is mi a' siubhal an lìn?


;No. Firefox only requests a location when a website makes a request, and only shares your location when the user has approved the request. Firefox does not track or remember your location as you browse.
Chan eil. Chan iarr Firefox ionad ach ma dh'iarras làrach-lìn e agus cha nochd e d' ionad mur an doir thusa cead dha Firefox a nochdadh. Cha dèan Firefox tracadh ort is cha chuimhnich e d' ionad is tu a' siubhal an lìn.


;How do I undo a permission granted to a site?
Ciamar a bheir mi air falbh cead o làrach a thug mi cead dha roimhe?


;If you've given Firefox permission to always give your location to a site and later change your mind, you can easily revoke that permission. Here's how:
Ma thug thu cead dha Firefox d' ionad a nochdadh do làrach uair sam bith 's ma chuireas tu romhad a chaochladh an uairsin, tha e furasta an cead a thug thu a thoirt air falbh. Seo mar a nì thu sin:


;Navigate to the site to which you’ve given permission
Tadhail air an làrach a thug thu cead dha roimhe


;Go to the <em>Tools</em> menu, then select <em>Page Info</em>
Fosgail clàr-taice nan <em>Innealan</em> is tagh <em>Fiosrachadh na duilleige</em>


;Select the <em>Permissions</em> tab
Tagh taba nan <em>Ceadan</em>


;Change the setting for <em>Share Location</em>
Atharraich an roghainn <em>Co-roinn an t-ionad</em>


;How do I clear the “random client identification number”?
Ciamar a bheir mi air falbh an "àireamh aithneachadh cliaint air thuaiream"?


;Go to the <em>Tools</em> menu, then select <em>Clear Recent History</em>
Fosgail clàr-taice nan <em>Innealan</em> is tagh <em>Falamhaich an eachdraidh faisg ort</em>


;Click the <em>Details</em> arrow
Briog air an t-saighead <em>Mion-fhiosrachadh</em>


;Ensure that <em>Cookies</em> is selected
Dèan cinnteach gun do thagh thu <em>Briosgaidean</em>


;Click on <em>Clear Now</em>
Briog air <em>Falamhaich an-dràsta</em>


;How do I turn off Location-Aware Browsing permanently?
Ciamar a chuireas mi dheth am brabhsadh a mhothaicheas dha m' ionad gu buan?


;Location-Aware Browsing is always opt-in in Firefox. No location information is ever sent without your permission. If you wish to disable the feature completely, please follow this set of steps:
Cha bhi brabhsadh a mhothaicheas ri d' àite air o thùs idir. Cha dèid fiosrachadh mu d' àite a chur a-null gun do chead idir. Ma tha thu airson am feart seo a chur dheth gu tur, dèan nan leanas:


;In the URL bar, type <code>about:config</code>
Cuir na leanas ann am bàr an URL:<code>about:config</code>


;Type <code>geo.enabled</code>
Cuir a-steach <code>geo.enabled</code>


;Double click on the <em>geo.enabled</em> preference
Dèan briogadh dùbailte air an roghainn <em>geo.enabled</em>


;Location-Aware Browsing is now disabled
Tha brabhsadh a mhothaicheas dha d' àite dheth a-nis


